            "title": "全球綠債發行7.4萬億破頂",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"全球綠債發行7.4萬億破頂\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"480\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/l14Bp.cb3nK1SzZ8Bgg_OA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTQ4MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-12/e89e2cb0-e2df-11f0-ad3e-e0acd95f7c2a\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">全球綠債發行7.4萬億破頂</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
