        {
            "title": "恒生新人力總監：盼培養雄心與關懷",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"恒生新人力總監：盼培養雄心與關懷\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Bwi59Prcy79MyR0ruYpuYw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-10/0718af40-a653-11f0-9ffd-0bfce509252c\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">恒生新人力總監：盼培養雄心與關懷</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%81%92%E7%94%9F%E6%96%B0%E4%BA%BA%E5%8A%9B%E7%B8%BD%E7%9B%A3-%E7%9B%BC%E5%9F%B9%E9%A4%8A%E9%9B%84%E5%BF%83%E8%88%87%E9%97%9C%E6%87%B7-181600906.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-27 12:45:39",
